  conclusion = compliant with USP <467> Option 2 and ICH Q3C.
- If unresolved warnings/manual-review items exist:
  conclusion = assessment generated with unresolved items; final compliance cannot be concluded until manual review is complete.
- Never claim full compliance if:
  unmapped_components not empty
  unresolved_evidence_items not empty
  q.s. solvent-like/process-aid amount missing
  ambiguous solvent evidence exists
  missing total equivalent ppm exists
- Option 2 basis:
  Use drug_product_amount_max_dose_mg to determine total daily intake basis.
  If daily intake > 10 g/day or approved/template requires Option 2, use PDE-based comparison.
- Populate summary:
  - calculated total exposure per solvent
  - PDE/USP <467> limit
  - pass/fail
  - unresolved warnings if any
- Do not hardcode compliance.

